_sText:
Welcome to Fy_Buckshot_Breakfloor!

This map is all in the name.  Its a bit of a fight arena/shotty map, and a bit of breakfloor all mixed in one.  

This was a quick build because I was bored, and I wanted to make a fun map that all could enjoy.  It is quite addicting, well, at least to me it is!

Start:
M3 Shotgun
Grenade
Deagle
(All are fully loaded to begin with)

There is HDR in this map, it is slighty hard to notice, but hey, I don't like overdoing things anyway.  It adds a nice touch.

Hope you all enjoy!
